properties.areaDesc: Cuyama Valley; San Luis Obispo County Mountains; San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 1 at 4:09PM PST until February 3 at 12:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest to north winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to
50 mph expected.

* WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys, Cuyama Valley
and San Luis Obispo County Mountains.

* WHEN...From 4 PM Sunday to noon PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strongest winds Sunday night.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM SUNDAY TO NOON PST MONDAY
